modules.description: Provides functions to retrieve the SIM card's country code, operator name, and service state. Works with string and integer types representing network information. Used to display carrier details or check network connectivity status in mobile applications.

The module provides functions to extract structured details from a `result` type, focusing on SIM card attributes, network states, and device identifiers, while handling callbacks for error and success scenarios. It operates on types representing phone states, SIM information, and permissions, enabling low-level access to mobile device data. Use cases include retrieving carrier details, monitoring network connectivity, and assessing SIM card status in mobile applications.
